Happy Heavenly Birthday Dad🕊️. Today he would’ve been 54. It’s been 6 months without you. And i miss you more every day. It feels like it’s been forever since I’ve seen and talked to you. My heart is still and forever crushed knowing i won’t be able to talk to you again in my lifetime. It hurts knowing my Dad will never see me walk down the aisle, no father daughter dance, meet my children. No more Christmas’ together, birthdays, holidays, and any other life events, big or small, really, really sucks. And this is all because a selfish drunk chose to get behind the wheel. Wouldn’t wish this pain upon anyone. Hug your loved ones close. Miss you more than anything in the world, Dad😔🤍
